stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IntentCreated
    IntentCreated --> Authorized: policy allow or valid approval
    IntentCreated --> Rejected: policy deny or approval rejected
    Authorized --> Submitted: send with idempotency key
    Submitted --> Committed: confirmed success
    Submitted --> Unknown: timeout or response lost
    Unknown --> Committed: reconciliation confirms effect
    Unknown --> NotCommitted: reconciliation confirms no effect
    Unknown --> ManualReview: cannot reconcile automatically
    NotCommitted --> Submitted: bounded retry with same key
    ManualReview --> Committed: evidence confirms effect
    ManualReview --> NotCommitted: evidence confirms no effect
    Rejected --> [*]
    Committed --> [*]
